      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every curve is polished to perfection, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, responsive, and incredibly quiet. It\u2019s rare to find one kept in such pristine shape, but I\u2019m ready to pass the keys to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look; you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
