    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a truly specimen-grade example, this machine has been meticulously dialed for the discerning driver. The powertrain exhibits flawless compression across all cylinders, paired with a buttery-smooth 6-speed gate that rewards precise rev-matching. We\u2019ve addressed every potential failure point\u2014from reinforced subframe mounting points to a complete VANOS overhaul with cryo-treated components. The suspension geometry is laser-aligned to minimize bushing deflection, ensuring surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically synchronized masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance and a chassis that feels tighter than the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 49750.0,
